query:
SELECT p.id, s.name as service_name, p.apiId, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice, p.updatedAt
FROM prices p
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Outros%' AND p.apiId = 2
ORDER BY p.updatedAt DESC
LIMIT 3;
